# Implementation Plan — Multimodal Earnings Call Intelligence System

## Team

| Member | Role | Domain |
|--------|------|--------|
| **Devasya** | Data Foundation & Preprocessing | Dataset collection, WhisperX, pyannote, structural labeling, Parquet/DuckDB |
| **Aadi** | Audio & Multimodal Modeling | openSMILE, wav2vec2, audio quality, feature fusion, interaction features |
| **Vansh** | Text NLP & Evaluation | FinBERT, sentiment features, LightGBM/XGBoost, leakage control, backtesting, reporting |

---

## How Parallel Work Is Achieved

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Zero-Dependency Principle:** Each member works on their own vertical pipeline. To prevent blocking, we use two techniques:
> 1. **Data Contracts** — In Phase 1, all three agree on exact Parquet column schemas (column names, types, sample values). Everyone codes to the contract, not to each other's pipeline.
> 2. **Mock Data** — Each member generates a small mock dataset in the agreed schema during Phase 1. This lets everyone develop and test their pipeline end-to-end without waiting for real upstream data.
>
> Real data integration happens only at defined **Sync Points** (end of Phase 2 and Phase 4).

