## Data Contracts (Agreed in Phase 1)

These are the Parquet schemas that all three members code against. They are defined **before** any real data exists.

### Contract A: `segments.parquet` (Devasya → Aadi, Vansh)

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `call_id` | `str` | Unique earnings call identifier (e.g., `AAPL_2024Q1`) |
| `segment_id` | `str` | Unique segment identifier within a call |
| `speaker_role` | `str` | One of: `ceo`, `cfo`, `analyst`, `operator`, `other` |
| `segment_type` | `str` | One of: `prepared_remarks`, `analyst_question`, `management_answer`, `operator_transition` |
| `text` | `str` | Cleaned transcript text for this segment |
| `start_time` | `float` | Segment start time in seconds |
| `end_time` | `float` | Segment end time in seconds |
| `audio_path` | `str` | Relative file path to the segment's audio chunk (WAV, 16kHz mono) |

### Contract B: `text_features.parquet` (Vansh → Vansh for modeling)

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `segment_id` | `str` | FK to `segments.parquet` |
| `sentiment_score` | `float` | FinBERT sentiment (-1 to +1) |
| `uncertainty_score` | `float` | Ratio of uncertainty language tokens |
| `forward_looking_score` | `float` | Ratio of forward-looking language tokens |
| `hedging_frequency` | `float` | Ratio of hedging tokens |
| `specificity_score` | `float` | `(numeric_tokens + named_entities) / total_tokens` |
| `linguistic_complexity` | `float` | Readability / syntactic complexity metric |

### Contract C: `audio_features.parquet` (Aadi → Vansh for modeling)

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `segment_id` | `str` | FK to `segments.parquet` |
| `pitch_mean` | `float` | Mean F0 (Hz) |
| `pitch_variance` | `float` | Variance of F0 |
| `speech_rate` | `float` | Syllables per second |
| `pause_duration_total` | `float` | Total silence duration in seconds |
| `energy_variance` | `float` | Variance of RMS energy |
| `voice_stability` | `float` | Jitter/shimmer-based stability score |
| `opensmile_vector` | `list[float]` | eGeMAPS feature vector (88 dimensions) |
| `wav2vec2_embedding` | `list[float]` | wav2vec2 mean-pooled embedding (768 dimensions) |

### Contract D: `market_data.parquet` (Devasya → Vansh for modeling)

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `call_id` | `str` | FK to `segments.parquet` |
| `ticker` | `str` | Stock ticker symbol |
| `call_date` | `date` | Date the earnings call occurred |
| `close_t0` | `float` | Closing price on call date |
| `close_t1` | `float` | Closing price next trading day |
| `close_t5` | `float` | Closing price 5 trading days later |
| `realized_vol_1d` | `float` | Next-day realized volatility |
| `realized_vol_5d` | `float` | 5-day realized volatility |
| `earnings_surprise` | `float` | `(reported - expected) / expected` |

